ym, co pozwoli na lepsze zarz\u0105dzanie bud\u017cetem.<\/li>\n<p> \u2013 Dobrze zaplanowane <a href=\"\/?p=6095\">programy lojalno\u015bciowe<\/a> mog\u0105 zwi\u0119kszy\u0107 sprzeda\u017c przy jednoczesnej redukcji koszt\u00f3w pozyskania nowych klient\u00f3w.<\/p>\n<li><b>Utrzymuj relacje z klientami<\/b><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Podsumowuj\u0105c, aby poprawi\u0107 rentowno\u015b\u0107, skup si\u0119 na redukcji koszt\u00f3w oraz strategicznym wydatkowaniu na reklam\u0119. Oba te dzia\u0142ania powinny by\u0107 zgodne z Twoimi celami finansowymi. <\/p>\n<p><b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h2>Jak zwi\u0119kszy\u0107 rentowno\u015b\u0107 w bran\u017cy Beauty i FMCG?<\/h2>\n<p>Czy zastanawia\u0142e\u015b si\u0119, jak poprawi\u0107 rento<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":3651,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[2],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-3650","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-kontent"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3650"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3650"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3650\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3651"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3650"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-jso